headline: 2 Truck Stocks to Keep an Eye on Despite Industry Headwinds
summary: The Zacks Industry Rank for the Transportation-Truck industry paints a dull picture, mainly owing to the slowdown in freight demand. We believe stocks like JBHT and SAIA are better positioned to escape industry challenges.
